Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.64,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your contract with us was through next year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your plans after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a job waiting for you back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing... yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Well, I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there is the first star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Seijiro-san... What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a string hanging from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A string?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could this string have come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:54.07,EP Title BG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2100,3170)\p1\blur1}m 0 0 l 950 0 950 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.18,0:02:54.06,EP Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,3200)\be1}String from the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There... there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There... there... stop crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go home until you stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the sky is filled with stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to that star?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The one with the long tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, did you really see one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The long-tailed star? Yes, last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way was it headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was zigzagging as it blinked on and off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if such a comet exits...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it did, it'd be a great discovery...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm definitely going to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name was Fuki, right? Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end... I never found such a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki came to us to care for my fretful youngest sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she would sometimes\N say such mysterious things,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,some people in the village looked\N upon Fuki with disdain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Master, she's not around here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've looked enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She must've grown tired of babysitting and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That ingrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, Fuki would never abandon her responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She attempted to grasp a string on the riverbank
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then disappeared right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Seijiro, if you want to help her, you really should come up with a better excuse for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in heaven's name have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}walking with him in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink it and get better quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be looking after you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to return to the way you were, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been affected by a powerful mushi influence and have become extremely ambiguous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people probably can't even see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That white string growing out of your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Touching it was probably the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Left as is, you'll drift farther and\N farther away from being a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... trying to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm just doing what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... well, you'll just have to bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Your color is looking a little better...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll look for a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll recover faster if you're around people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If your memory doesn't come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,stay at a nearby village for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, which way should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something glowing inside the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... In your current condition,\Nyou can probably see it very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that we're on the path of the light vein.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that's glowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called {\i1}Kouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Schools of embryonic mushi swimming together...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you mean those tiny things that lay quietly in the shadows or float about in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... They're lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stare at them so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That glow is poison to the eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you become too accustomed to it, you'll become unable to see sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a river of light in the sky, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at night, it glows by the light of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that river instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though I were looking at a reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're similar, but not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't look at the wrong one by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I slept well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The little mistress didn't cry last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I have to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your memory returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My village is at the foot of that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... Fuki, aren't you? The one who disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.32,Alt,,0,0,0,,It's Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the mountains all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We all searched the mountains thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just pulled on a string dangling from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything around me went black.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go with that nonsense again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you run away but come back\Nbecause you were frightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too late now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Master already hired someone to replace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seijiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine... That man helped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come to my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you already have a replacement...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come back as my bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was determined to ask you when you came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absurd! I won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to keep you waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to go talk to him?\N Sounded like you two were arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect him to approve right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear how Fuki disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you'll believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, Fuki said she saw \Na string dangling from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and motioned as though she \Nwere grasping at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In that instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki whisked upwards into the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...and disappeared into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No one believes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I saw it happen, even I thought that the things Fuki claimed to see
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,were just figments of her imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... That's {\i1}Tenpengusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're mushi that live high up in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Born from yin, they gather at the border with yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki described them as tiny things
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that lay quietly in the shadows or float about in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Few people can see them, but they exist in every corner of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see what Fuki sees?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I make my living from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I... envy you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki is a lucky woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But watch out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She still is not completely free of the mushi's influence...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tenpengusa{\i0} normally appear as \Nballoon-like objects with a tail
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and move about in the skies above special ground called the path of the light vein.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They live by feeding on feebly\N luminescent mushi in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at night, they also appear like\N stars weaving through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they're also known as wayward stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That way... It was zigzagging as it blinked on and off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This rarely happens, but when \Nthere isn't enough food in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,they extend their tentacles down near the ground like dropping a fishing line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a string.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When an animal makes contact, \Nit reels the animal skyward,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but then spits it out high in the sky because it is unable to swallow it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Most times, the prey falls to the ground and dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but Fuki was fortunate to get\Ncaught in a tree, so she survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But perhaps because she was partially swallowed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki became greatly affected by the mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was why you couldn't find her when you searched the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki had turned into something\Nhuman eyes could not see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This medicine has helped her recover considerably,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's still not completely cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still connected to the sky by the string on her hand and remains in an unstable condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So if things go wrong, it'll happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki requires more than just this medicine to return to being human again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She also needs to feel that she \Nwants to remain a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} must make her feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it's none of my business...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take your words to heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not stay a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stay any longer than I already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be holding our wedding \Nin the near future for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be sure to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? You don't have to bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But we owe you our thanks for everything, Ginko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, I'll drop by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I later received a letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1307)\i1}It said Fuki had disappeared once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My old man just wouldn't give us his blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Day after day, I tried to change his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And Fuki felt miserable the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As that went on, Fuki's body gradually became lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So light that the breeze would\Nsend her floating up into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And as the days went by, she became\Nunable to stay on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki, please come on down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to come down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've almost got Father convinced,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but if he sees you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My body floats up by itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to take your medicine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But then one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've looked everywhere, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that {\i1}you{\i0} had to keep her tie to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I did try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to get others to accept Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But with her the way she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More than anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you are unable to accept Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you rejected her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,she became unable to maintain human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to... maintain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but Fuki is still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to lose Fuki, accept who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You say to accept her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But how, when I can't even see or touch her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably the reason why she's barely still around here even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:19:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What... what should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Seijiro... Why do you always gaze at the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I wonder myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when unpleasant things happen during the day, the stars never fail to appear at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel calm for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too... When I feel sad because \Nthe little mistress won't stop crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I take my mind off of it by counting the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So when dawn's light appears, I somehow feel lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of stars gets smaller and smaller...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you know it, there isn't a single one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do they all go during the daytime?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so silly, Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are still there in the sky even during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The sunlight is too strong for us to see them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're actually still up in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So they don't go anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...even if we can't see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're still up in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They said it was the strangest of sights...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wedding was hastily held
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}without the bride being present.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Despite that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Fuki, it's your turn to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the groom behaved as though his bride were there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this way is better...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seeing him act that way, people whispered that the groom, too, had lost his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Day passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and he took up his residence alone \Non the outskirts of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As always, he conversed with\N his wife who wasn't there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eventually, the villagers stopped coming around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But as time passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Seijiro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Fuki. When did she come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People began to see Fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say that ever since then, Fuki's habit of disappearing never returned.
